    {
      "role": "user",
      "content": "i was just staring at the stars and it hit me. nothing we do actually matters. like, in a billion years the sun is gone and the universe is just cold and dead. everything we feel, every struggle, every stupid little achievement... it's all just a temporary glitch in the void. it feels so pointless to even keep trying.",
